Package: ginko
Title: Cluster And Network Word Analysis Of Scientific Papers
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Matthias Nachtmann, Lisa Gotzian, Prabesh Dhakal
Maintainer: Lisa Gotzian <lisa.gotzian@stud.leuphana.de>
Description: Analyzes large amounts of (scientific) text, usually your own pdf
    files or automatically downloaded abstracts from Scopus.com. Analyzes them
    using indicator values and clustering or network analysis. Includes easy-
    to-grasp graphics.
